summary: here’s the thing though guys. i have never seen anyone look at each other the way dan and phil look at each other. not online or...
body: here’s the thing though guys. i have never seen anyone look at each other the way dan and phil look at each other. not online or irl, like literally never. they just have so much love in their eyes when the interact. you can see it all over their faces. i’m sure there are people out there that do, but i’ve never seen it. so for me, it’s not just ‘shipping’, it’s supporting such a true genuine love and companionship because the world could really use some more of that.
